{"kind":"image","id":"im/bm9wf65c","slide":4,"name":"图片 12","alt":"Fig. 7 periodic subband-filter coefficients","bbox":[54.37,318.47,451.34,359.96]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/jyx0ra1s","slide":4,"text":"这里把瓶颈归纳为失真和混叠两类，并说明论文的理论分析要把 T、L、D 和原型滤波器放在同一框架中。"}
